code: - (UIButton *)titleButton {if (!_titleButton) {_titleButton = [UIButton buttonWithType:UIButtonTypeCustom];[_titleButton setTitle:@"选择游戏" forState:UIControlStateNormal];_titleButton.titleLabel.font = TGFontBold(24.0f);[_titleButton setTitleColor:UIColor.whiteColor forState:UIControlStateNormal];[_titleButton addTarget:self action:@selector(presentPickGameVC) forControlEvents:UIControlEventTouchUpInside];[_titleButton setContentHorizontalAlignment:UIControlContentHorizontalAlignmentCenter];[_titleButton setImage:[[UIImage imageNamed:@"nav_game_change_clear"] imageByTintColor:UIColor.whiteColor] forState:UIControlStateNormal];}return _titleButton;}
